# pythonic

n = int(input())
m = int(input())
stickers = list(map(int, input().split()))

album = [False] * n
repetidas = []

for s in stickers:
    i = s - 1
    if album[i]:
        repetidas.append(s)
    else:
        album[i] = True

faltantes = [str(i + 1) for i in range(n) if not album[i]]

print(" ".join(map(str, repetidas)) if repetidas else "N")
print(" ".join(faltantes) if faltantes else "N")
